{"url": "https://people.com/style/bee-shaffer-marries-francesco-carrozzini-second-ceremony-italy/", "text": "The fashion fairytale continues!\n\nOne week after Bee Shaffer, daughter of Vogue editor-in-chief Anna Wintour, married Italian film director Francesco Carrozzini, son of the late Vogue Italia\u2019s editor-in-chief Franca Sozzani, in a Long Island ceremony, the two had a second wedding ceremony in Portofino, Italy.\n\nThe couple said \u201cI do\u201d for the second time in front of a small group of friends and family, including Carrozzini\u2019s aunt, Carla Sozzani (sister of his mother) in the town\u2019s San Giorgio church.\n\nBecause of the couple\u2019s strict no social media policy during their first wedding, this is the first time we\u2019ve officially seen Shaffer in a wedding gown. The bride chose an ivory V-neck lace gown with a tea-length skirt and matching lace veil. She accessorized with a cross necklace and gold strappy sandals.\n\nBACKGRID\n\nThe groom wore a navy double-breasted suit with brown loafers.\n\nWhile it\u2019s still unknown what dress design Shaffer wore for her first nuptials, there are rumors it\u2019s being kept under wraps until it can be unveiled in an upcoming Vogue issue.\n\nNeilson Barnard/Getty Images\n\nAccording to WWD, the couple visited Sozzani\u2019s grave after the ceremony. Carrozzini changed into jeans and a T-shirt for the visit, while Shaffer remained in her lace dress but took off her veil.\n\nThe couple confirmed their engagement to PEOPLE in March 2017 and two months later, Shaffer showed off her engagement ring for the first time on the Met Gala red carpet.", "images": ["https://people.com/thmb/ADbPiyx0RoIJfEi38L9MQMMI_Lw=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(599x0:601x2)/bee-7030f87cfba040c19e2694a68673cecc.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/t7iAAGrVBDDlcisB8oZhYld5K7E=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(611x0:613x2)/rihanna21-035ca9aedbeb4389bbc3be19e4d5cf6d.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/g24mvJWoa4q58e10PAmMcLZlVrM=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(593x485:595x487)/melissa-gilbert-345b8a9f03ec45c3bbd421583bd1ddcb.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/2BYo0nzNyx9IgyHwVoUfm-YVsbY=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(734x219:736x221)/kim-kardashian-2-d8690a3cc13843ad828bab22fb4e047d.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/PBv78GfHjnZBwn8gCMIvLdBCN-A=/650x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(741x0:743x2)/bee-shaffer-b-2000-5928eb057dcf4c0f99b7e98b6a1386ab.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/u783cmHD6ei7GAR_TPxIld_qQIE=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(593x359:595x361)/kourtney-kardashian-travis-barker_1-2000-a11c0b4904e64143861c7843885e6043.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/Lje7sGaj3HgeS-yLg9z5JSNPfrU=/300x150/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/people_magazine_sub-e6689738996d40f38f154099e1751481.png", "https://people.com/thmb/fPPn4HOdGS528S1790Cx4GYL0ow=/650x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(665x0:667x2)/bee-shaffer-2000-035741fd100844a595488bb5282883b4.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/Sm4gaoxlZ0P9xC4JY45gc7mZwyk=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(585x284:587x286)/kate-bock-15-e24ba5f4425045c18b94cc4d046731ab.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/DE_hEkeUJgJQbe-g2BTV-6gG1VA=/1333x2000/filters:fill(auto,1)/bee-shaffer-2000-035741fd100844a595488bb5282883b4.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/j75yax97BE2snPP-BqkF_2LGkJw=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(649x0:651x2)/kardashians-jenners-7e376445ba60402898e9226f890ed0ef.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/21rGQsvs084iXTY7n0IWnG7zw1w=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(749x0:751x2)/Britney-Spears-and-Sam-Asghari-Wedding-Dress-and-Tuxedo-Sketch-1ca49903017742638e96df256f23cfed.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/jYYVBjEozgU0Td_KqU9yxc_Ju7Y=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_byt